HEADWORD: niobium
<hw>ni*o"bi*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr. L. & E.
<er>Niobe</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>The chemical element of
